      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm studying for usmle and i'm a bit stuck on differential counts. can u explain the difference between neutrophilia and lymphocytosis when looking at acute vs chronic infections? like what's the main takeaway for the boards?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
