    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "could u explain the role of cytokines in this? like, if there's an intense battle going on at the tissue level, what specific signals are being sent to call in the reinforcements? just trying to wrap my head around the \"battlefield\" dynamics of how the cells actually get there.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
